WEBVTT

01:27.390 --> 01:31.890
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.160 --> 01:34.940
[Episode 15]

01:35.020 --> 01:38.229
[Xinsheng International Law Firm]

01:38.590 --> 01:41.000
Ding Zhibo and Oceanvision International
had a lawyer's letter sent to you,

01:41.000 --> 01:43.070
purely out
of public relations considerations—

01:43.070 --> 01:45.590
they're trying to deny
the allegations completely.

01:45.590 --> 01:46.640
But I don't believe

01:46.640 --> 01:48.280
they'll actually sue.

01:48.920 --> 01:50.789
You didn't film or share

01:50.789 --> 01:51.990
those videos online,

01:52.350 --> 01:52.840
so your actions do not constitute

01:52.840 --> 01:55.350
the required elements
for a defamation lawsuit.

01:55.350 --> 01:58.080
The court most likely
won't even accept the case.

01:58.950 --> 02:00.010
Thank you, Senior.

02:00.920 --> 02:01.760
The things

02:02.350 --> 02:03.550
you said in the video,

02:03.920 --> 02:04.920
are they all true?

02:12.520 --> 02:13.960
In that case, their public lawyer's letter
on social media

02:13.960 --> 02:15.680
actually constitutes

02:15.680 --> 02:17.410
defamation against you.

02:17.800 --> 02:18.680
If you'd like,

02:18.680 --> 02:19.740
I can represent you

02:19.800 --> 02:21.130
and file a countersuit.

02:23.910 --> 02:25.410
But if we countersue,

02:25.710 --> 02:27.910
they probably won't just let it go, right?

02:27.910 --> 02:30.470
Ding Zhibo is now categorically
denying everything.

02:30.470 --> 02:32.400
But once we fight back

02:32.560 --> 02:33.520
and he realizes

02:33.800 --> 02:35.430
he can't just walk away,

02:36.190 --> 02:37.720
his next move will likely be

02:38.280 --> 02:39.750
smearing you

02:40.400 --> 02:41.860
and vilifying the victim.

02:43.000 --> 02:44.360
It's their standard playbook:

02:44.360 --> 02:46.120
we've seen many such cases.

02:47.120 --> 02:47.920
Smearing her?

02:48.560 --> 02:49.240
Basically,

02:49.960 --> 02:51.910
they'll attack Yan Ling's character

02:51.910 --> 02:54.560
and spread fabricated "facts"

02:54.870 --> 02:56.840
to undermine public trust in you.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.360
That's exactly the kind of dramatic twist

02:58.360 --> 02:59.690
the online crowd loves.

03:00.870 --> 03:01.930
If it comes to that,

03:02.310 --> 03:04.560
it would only retraumatize the victim.

03:08.280 --> 03:09.710
I can't be

03:10.280 --> 03:11.740
Ding Zhibo's only victim.

03:13.290 --> 03:15.520
Isn't there any way the law
can hold him accountable?

03:15.520 --> 03:17.000
I've heard that the police

03:17.000 --> 03:18.190
have already started

03:18.190 --> 03:20.000
investigating their charity foundation,

03:20.000 --> 03:21.560
but someone like Ding Zhibo,
who's been around for a long time,

03:21.560 --> 03:23.220
is definitely very cautious.

03:23.590 --> 03:24.720
Just like this time,

03:24.960 --> 03:27.150
he most likely took the children abroad,

03:27.150 --> 03:28.840
which has made the investigation
even harder.

03:28.840 --> 03:29.970
Moreover, he's very good

03:29.970 --> 03:31.770
at covering up his crimes,

03:32.150 --> 03:33.880
and the victims' sense of shame

03:34.030 --> 03:35.150
will be even stronger.

03:35.150 --> 03:36.640
Not everyone has your courage

03:36.640 --> 03:38.470
to speak out and identify him.

03:44.910 --> 03:46.400
It's not about courage.

03:49.750 --> 03:50.560
To be honest,

03:51.030 --> 03:51.560
Yan Ling,

03:54.310 --> 03:55.710
I used to look down on you.

03:57.710 --> 03:59.030
Back in school,

03:59.750 --> 04:01.150
when I saw him pick you up,

04:02.560 --> 04:03.800
I naively assumed

04:05.560 --> 04:07.000
you were the kind of girl

04:07.590 --> 04:08.920
people gossiped about.

04:10.470 --> 04:11.430
Until now,

04:11.520 --> 04:13.450
after these recent interactions,

04:13.680 --> 04:15.630
especially throughout this incident
with Ding Zhibo,

04:15.630 --> 04:16.760
I've come to realize

04:16.920 --> 04:18.120
I was wrong

04:18.120 --> 04:20.250
to believe such a one-sided illusion.

04:21.360 --> 04:21.959
I'm sorry—

04:23.160 --> 04:24.750
for my arrogance back then,

04:25.430 --> 04:27.160
and for my mean-spiritedness.

04:29.160 --> 04:30.360
You don't have to decide

04:30.360 --> 04:31.760
right now whether to sue.

04:31.920 --> 04:33.120
Whenever you're ready,

04:33.120 --> 04:34.120
just say the word.

04:39.240 --> 04:40.700
No matter what you decide,

04:41.040 --> 04:42.100
I've got your back.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.120
You two...

04:45.800 --> 04:47.200
Is that what I think it is?

04:50.920 --> 04:51.560
Senior,

04:53.040 --> 04:54.700
these are our wedding sweets.

04:55.800 --> 04:56.070
I

04:56.680 --> 04:58.240
knew something was up

04:58.240 --> 04:59.040
the first time

05:00.510 --> 05:01.770
I saw you two together.

05:12.000 --> 05:13.860
Alright, we're home.

05:19.510 --> 05:20.160
Honey,

05:21.070 --> 05:21.870
I'm starving.

05:22.510 --> 05:25.120
What do you think Mom will
have cooked for us tonight?

05:25.120 --> 05:26.480
I bet she will have made braised pork.

05:26.480 --> 05:27.270
Really?

05:27.270 --> 05:31.070
-I casually acted cute this morning...
-You asked for it this morning.

05:31.070 --> 05:34.720
-and she took it seriously.
-I think she likes you more than me now.

05:34.720 --> 05:35.480
Okay.

05:40.600 --> 05:41.720
It's the hospital's call.

05:41.720 --> 05:42.650
Let me answer it.

05:43.120 --> 05:44.180
I'll head upstairs and wait for you.

05:44.180 --> 05:44.750
Sounds good.

05:44.750 --> 05:45.430
Hurry up.

05:51.040 --> 05:52.300
Why are you calling me?

05:52.480 --> 05:53.290
We're busted.

05:53.680 --> 05:55.010
She spotted me just now.

05:55.070 --> 05:55.670
Who was it?

05:56.240 --> 05:57.440
Your mother-in-law.

05:57.630 --> 05:58.600
It just happened,

05:58.600 --> 06:00.530
at my supermarket on Dongtai Road.

06:03.520 --> 06:05.250
I told you to lay low for a while.

06:06.040 --> 06:07.300
What did she say to you?

06:07.900 --> 06:09.480
She asked when I got back.

06:12.070 --> 06:13.270
What did you tell her?

06:15.560 --> 06:16.720
I just said,

06:17.070 --> 06:18.800
"You've got the wrong person."

06:19.040 --> 06:19.630
Got it.

06:56.920 --> 06:57.630
Yan Ling...

06:57.909 --> 06:58.350
Mom,

06:59.950 --> 07:01.000
what are you up to?

07:02.420 --> 07:03.920
What were you two talking about?

07:03.920 --> 07:05.120
N-Nothing much.

07:05.430 --> 07:07.690
I was just looking for a pair of scissors.

07:08.950 --> 07:10.880
Do you know where the scissors are?

07:11.040 --> 07:13.240
Mom wants to make a photo wall for Jiale.

07:15.120 --> 07:16.360
There's a pair in the study.

07:16.360 --> 07:17.420
I'll get it for you.

07:17.680 --> 07:18.240
Sure.

07:18.560 --> 07:19.310
Go get changed first.

07:19.310 --> 07:19.750
Okay.

07:33.680 --> 07:34.070
Mom.

07:42.720 --> 07:45.780
Look how adorable Jiale was
in these childhood photos.

07:47.070 --> 07:48.810
I've been here for a couple of days now—

07:48.810 --> 07:49.680
how come you haven't

07:49.680 --> 07:50.720
called your mom?

07:52.600 --> 07:54.060
I called her a few days ago.

07:54.360 --> 07:56.510
She mentioned my aunt
isn't recovering well after surgery,

07:56.510 --> 07:59.640
so she's been staying
at the hospital to take care of her.

08:02.360 --> 08:02.800
Mom,

08:04.360 --> 08:06.490
did you need something from my mother?

08:08.110 --> 08:09.560
No, nothing in particular.

08:09.560 --> 08:11.020
I've been thinking of her.

08:14.510 --> 08:15.000
Mom,

08:16.000 --> 08:17.200
the lawyer said today

08:17.750 --> 08:20.120
that the court won't accept
Ding Zhibo's lawsuit.

08:20.120 --> 08:21.920
You don't need to worry anymore.

08:24.120 --> 08:24.720
What?

08:25.560 --> 08:26.760
You already told Mom?

08:27.480 --> 08:28.000
Not yet.

08:28.920 --> 08:29.800
Mom was just asking

08:29.800 --> 08:32.600
how my aunt's recovery
is going after the surgery.

08:37.750 --> 08:38.750
Wow, something

08:39.480 --> 08:40.409
smells amazing.

08:41.909 --> 08:42.270
Mom,

08:42.840 --> 08:44.970
did you really make red-braised pork?

08:45.150 --> 08:46.550
You're way too good to me.

08:50.630 --> 08:51.270
Let's eat.

08:51.750 --> 08:52.200
Okay.

08:52.910 --> 08:53.510
Come on,

08:53.720 --> 08:54.520
I'm starving.

08:55.360 --> 08:56.020
Hurry over.

08:59.150 --> 09:00.550
There are so many dishes.

09:09.910 --> 09:11.170
Mom, you don't have to do all this—

09:11.170 --> 09:11.870
let me help.

09:12.830 --> 09:13.520
It's fine.

09:13.670 --> 09:15.130
Yan Ling can give me a hand.

09:15.420 --> 09:16.550
You're letting her help?

09:16.550 --> 09:17.210
Better not.

09:17.840 --> 09:19.170
Have you seen her nails?

09:20.360 --> 09:21.910
She's getting her wedding photos
taken tomorrow—

09:21.910 --> 09:23.840
she even got a manicure
for the first time ever.

09:23.840 --> 09:24.670
Do they look nice?

09:24.670 --> 09:27.330
Well, don't let her ruin them
by washing dishes.

09:27.960 --> 09:28.480
Honey,

09:28.750 --> 09:30.360
I think you should hurry up
and take a shower,

09:30.360 --> 09:30.960
then put on a face mask,

09:30.960 --> 09:32.960
so you'll look beautiful tomorrow.

09:35.550 --> 09:36.910
Then you help out more, okay?

09:36.910 --> 09:38.320
Don't let Mom overwork herself.

09:38.320 --> 09:38.850
Alright.

09:40.150 --> 09:42.210
Mom, I'm off to go pamper myself a bit.

10:02.040 --> 10:03.480
Typhoon No. 5 of the year

10:03.480 --> 10:05.440
is expected to make landfall
in our city tonight.

10:05.440 --> 10:07.550
China's National Meteorological Center
has issued a red warning.

10:07.550 --> 10:09.320
Heavy rain will continue
through tomorrow morning—

10:09.320 --> 10:12.250
residents are advised
to avoid unnecessary travel.

10:18.670 --> 10:19.720
But you know,

10:19.750 --> 10:22.360
I feel like my acting has
become much more relaxed lately.

10:22.360 --> 10:23.510
I'm not as nervous as I used to be.

10:23.510 --> 10:24.220
Oh really?

10:24.320 --> 10:25.380
We have a customer.

10:29.120 --> 10:29.840
Mrs. Luo,

10:30.840 --> 10:31.630
you're back.

10:38.120 --> 10:38.630
Mom.

10:40.620 --> 10:42.020
You're all here already!

10:42.600 --> 10:43.660
Welcome, welcome.

10:43.670 --> 10:44.240
Hello.

10:44.240 --> 10:44.550
Hello,

10:44.550 --> 10:45.680
Ms. Su.

11:22.490 --> 11:26.210
[General Higher Education
Graduation Certificate]

11:29.040 --> 11:32.060
[Name: Luo Liang]
[Collage: Tianfu Medical University]

11:35.120 --> 11:35.510
Mom,

11:36.320 --> 11:37.480
what are you looking for?

11:37.480 --> 11:38.550
Nothing, really.

11:39.390 --> 11:41.910
Just haven't finished
organizing all this yet.

11:41.910 --> 11:42.840
You should rest.

11:43.390 --> 11:45.050
I'll take care of it tomorrow.

11:45.600 --> 11:46.400
Alright then.

11:47.240 --> 11:47.630
Mom,

11:48.150 --> 11:50.160
you must be exhausted
from moving these past couple of days.

11:50.160 --> 11:52.420
Yan Ling wants me
to take good care of you.

11:52.550 --> 11:52.960
Mom,

11:54.150 --> 11:54.510
here,

11:55.240 --> 11:56.170
sit down please.

11:57.070 --> 11:58.060
Try this—

11:58.390 --> 11:59.850
it's really comfortable.

12:01.670 --> 12:02.500
Thank you.

12:02.700 --> 12:03.900
Is the pressure okay?

12:04.870 --> 12:05.670
It's perfect.

12:05.810 --> 12:06.300
Good.

12:07.360 --> 12:08.420
Is Yan Ling asleep?

12:08.480 --> 12:09.140
Yes, she is.

12:09.620 --> 12:12.020
She went to bed early
so she'll look her best

12:12.080 --> 12:13.940
for the wedding photos tomorrow.

12:23.630 --> 12:25.160
Earlier, while tidying up,

12:25.310 --> 12:26.980
I came across your diploma.

12:28.360 --> 12:28.720
Yeah,

12:29.440 --> 12:31.970
I entered Tianfu Medical University
in 2004.

12:32.030 --> 12:34.290
Getting into such a prestigious school—

12:34.320 --> 12:36.120
you must have been a top student.

12:36.550 --> 12:37.610
Yan Ling mentioned

12:38.020 --> 12:39.050
your father

12:39.510 --> 12:40.320
was once

12:40.840 --> 12:42.960
sent to work in Diannan
as an educated youth.

12:42.960 --> 12:45.560
And your mother seemed
so cultured the other day—

12:45.560 --> 12:47.220
was she an educated youth too?

12:47.240 --> 12:47.960
No,

12:49.030 --> 12:51.490
she worked as a health worker
in the commune.

12:52.200 --> 12:54.600
I saw your mother
at the supermarket today.

12:58.320 --> 12:59.450
That's impossible.

13:00.390 --> 13:01.670
You must have mistaken her
for someone else.

13:01.670 --> 13:03.530
She looked just like your mother—

13:03.550 --> 13:05.080
even her voice was the same.

13:05.870 --> 13:07.670
I gave her my contact number too.

13:08.510 --> 13:10.320
It must have been a case
of mistaken identity.

13:10.320 --> 13:12.320
She's in the Philippines right now—

13:12.400 --> 13:14.510
unless she can be in two places at once.

13:14.510 --> 13:16.370
I've been teaching my whole life,

13:17.550 --> 13:20.080
and I've never once
misidentified a student.

13:23.440 --> 13:26.100
Yan Ling has told you
everything about herself—

13:26.350 --> 13:28.150
she's given you her whole heart.

13:29.960 --> 13:30.600
I know.

13:31.480 --> 13:32.740
And I feel the same way.

13:34.660 --> 13:36.160
The most important thing

13:36.510 --> 13:38.570
between husband and wife is honesty.

13:38.950 --> 13:40.550
Yan Ling went through so much

13:40.840 --> 13:42.040
before she found you.

13:42.960 --> 13:44.270
I hope the two of you

13:44.270 --> 13:46.470
will cherish each other for a lifetime.

13:49.360 --> 13:51.290
She's suffered so much in the past,

13:54.630 --> 13:56.080
and I hate myself

13:56.080 --> 13:58.480
for not being able
to protect her back then.

14:00.320 --> 14:01.480
I swear.

14:02.800 --> 14:03.790
If anyone

14:04.080 --> 14:06.140
ever bullies or hurts her from now on,

14:06.320 --> 14:08.250
I will not let them get away with it.

14:14.510 --> 14:15.000
Mom,

14:16.760 --> 14:18.360
I've also made up my mind

14:18.760 --> 14:21.020
to spend the rest of my life
with Yan Ling.

14:25.280 --> 14:26.880
You should get some rest now—

14:27.240 --> 14:28.900
they say a typhoon is coming tomorrow

14:28.900 --> 14:29.950
with heavy rain.

14:32.750 --> 14:33.480
I'm going to check

14:33.480 --> 14:35.630
that all the windows
and doors are closed.

14:35.630 --> 14:36.690
Get to sleep early.

14:45.480 --> 14:45.840
Mom.

14:47.240 --> 14:47.900
Goodnight.

15:18.980 --> 15:20.720
[Name: Dai Si Sheng]
[Chengyu Education Bureau]

15:27.850 --> 15:30.400
[Name: Dai Si Sheng]
[Chengyu Education Bureau]

15:35.250 --> 15:35.870
Hello,

15:36.120 --> 15:37.050
is this Si Sheng?

15:37.360 --> 15:38.000
It's me,

15:38.120 --> 15:38.750
Ms. Su.

15:40.960 --> 15:41.360
Hello?

15:42.630 --> 15:43.360
Yes, it's me.

15:44.600 --> 15:45.480
I wanted to ask—

15:45.960 --> 15:46.790
are you still

15:47.480 --> 15:50.320
working at the Chengyu Education Bureau?

15:50.820 --> 15:51.830
That's great.

15:53.030 --> 15:54.890
Could you help me look up a student

15:55.150 --> 15:56.480
from your Tianfu Medical University,

15:56.480 --> 15:58.140
named Luo Liang?

15:59.320 --> 16:00.980
She's already figured it out.

16:01.880 --> 16:02.640
I think

16:03.750 --> 16:05.410
you should arrange to meet her

16:05.480 --> 16:06.940
and be completely honest.

16:07.910 --> 16:09.870
Please send her a text later

16:10.830 --> 16:12.630
and ask to meet tomorrow at 10 AM,

16:12.910 --> 16:14.370
at that same supermarket.

16:16.250 --> 16:17.580
I appreciate your help.

16:17.740 --> 16:20.260
Let me know as soon as you find anything.

16:21.720 --> 16:22.280
Okay.

16:22.480 --> 16:23.940
Thanks for your hard work.

17:50.440 --> 17:50.960
Mom,

17:51.440 --> 17:51.960
don't trouble yourself.

17:51.960 --> 17:53.030
We don't have time to eat—

17:53.030 --> 17:54.370
we need to head out now.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.720
With the rain today, traffic might be bad.

17:55.720 --> 17:56.550
But I've already made breakfast.

17:56.550 --> 17:57.270
That's right.

17:57.270 --> 17:58.680
On a rainy day like this,
there's no need to go out for groceries.

17:58.680 --> 18:00.020
If you need anything,
just call us—

18:00.020 --> 18:01.750
we can pick it up on our way back.

18:01.960 --> 18:02.830
Right, Mom.

18:03.160 --> 18:04.180
Don't go outside.

18:04.310 --> 18:05.640
Just wait for us at home.

18:05.750 --> 18:08.160
But with such heavy rain,
can you still take photos?

18:08.160 --> 18:10.310
Yes, today's shoot is indoors.

18:12.830 --> 18:14.490
I'll take two marinated eggs.

18:14.640 --> 18:15.700
Wait for us at home.

18:20.030 --> 18:20.800
Hurry up!

18:21.000 --> 18:21.550
It tastes so good.

18:21.550 --> 18:22.580
We're going to be late.

18:22.580 --> 18:24.000
Mom's marinated eggs are amazing.

18:24.000 --> 18:24.660
Take a bite.

18:24.960 --> 18:26.480
Mom, wait for us at home, okay?

18:26.480 --> 18:27.350
Mom, we're heading out now.

18:27.350 --> 18:27.880
Hurry up!

18:40.670 --> 18:42.350
[Ms. Su, tomorrow at 10 AM,]

18:42.370 --> 18:44.020
[same supermarket, let's have a chat.]

19:47.340 --> 19:49.340
[Construction Ahead, No Entry]

21:09.870 --> 21:12.030
Every time there's a typhoon
or heavy rain here,

21:12.030 --> 21:14.480
we open the manhole covers
on the road for drainage.

21:14.480 --> 21:16.400
We always put up warning signs
to block off the road.

21:16.400 --> 21:18.110
It's been like this for many years,

21:18.110 --> 21:20.440
and the nearby residents all know
to take a detour.

21:20.440 --> 21:21.920
We're not sure if it was a prank

21:21.920 --> 21:23.070
or a work error,

21:23.480 --> 21:25.480
but the warning sign was misplaced—

21:25.860 --> 21:27.510
and our neighborhood office
failed to notice.

21:27.510 --> 21:28.370
We will conduct

21:28.480 --> 21:30.540
a thorough review of our procedures.

21:54.480 --> 21:55.140
Ms. Yan.

21:56.560 --> 21:57.310
Ms. Yan.

22:00.870 --> 22:01.800
Let me take that.

22:02.150 --> 22:03.750
These were her mother's belongings.

22:03.750 --> 22:04.400
According to the investigation,

22:04.400 --> 22:05.090
there is no surveillance
on the section of the road

22:05.090 --> 22:06.310
where the incident occurred.

22:06.310 --> 22:08.240
However, surveillance footage
from other sections

22:08.240 --> 22:09.200
shows

22:09.520 --> 22:10.240
that her mother

22:10.240 --> 22:11.970
was walking alone on that road.

22:12.440 --> 22:15.880
It's highly likely that her death
was an accidental drowning.

22:15.880 --> 22:16.750
Please accept our condolences.

22:16.750 --> 22:17.350
Thank you.

23:43.480 --> 23:44.340
Uncle, Auntie.

23:45.020 --> 23:45.810
You're back.

23:46.110 --> 23:47.240
Please, have a seat.

23:48.880 --> 23:49.750
She hasn't woken up, has she?

23:49.750 --> 23:50.550
No, not yet.

23:53.090 --> 23:54.550
She hadn't slept for days—

23:54.790 --> 23:56.880
she finally took a sleeping pill
to get some sleep.

23:56.880 --> 23:58.200
How's Jiale?

23:58.400 --> 23:59.350
Lu is with him.

23:59.790 --> 24:01.120
Jiale is so thoughtful.

24:01.200 --> 24:03.590
He said he wanted to stay
with Lu for a few days.

24:03.590 --> 24:05.070
He's worried that if he stayed with us,

24:05.070 --> 24:06.610
his mom will still have
to take care of him.

24:06.610 --> 24:08.540
What a wonderful family you are...

24:09.510 --> 24:11.910
Why did something like this
have to happen?

24:13.750 --> 24:14.590
Luo,

24:16.000 --> 24:18.120
if there's anything you need,
just say it.

24:18.120 --> 24:18.920
We see Yan Ling

24:19.000 --> 24:20.700
as our own daughter.

24:22.160 --> 24:23.160
Uncle, Auntie,

24:23.550 --> 24:25.410
your being here to watch over her—

24:25.550 --> 24:26.680
so I could go settle Jiale

24:26.680 --> 24:27.600
and get the phone repaired—

24:27.600 --> 24:29.200
has already been a huge help.

24:31.880 --> 24:34.010
I really shouldn't have left her side.

24:34.750 --> 24:35.950
I really wanted to fix

24:36.760 --> 24:38.290
her mother's phone for her—

24:39.110 --> 24:41.510
it would mean a lot,
something to hold on to.

24:41.550 --> 24:43.410
You're very considerate.

24:44.000 --> 24:45.160
With you by her side,

24:45.750 --> 24:46.750
Yan Ling's mother

24:47.160 --> 24:48.350
can rest easy.

24:49.200 --> 24:50.550
Now that you're back,

24:52.160 --> 24:53.290
we should head home.

24:53.680 --> 24:54.740
We'll be going now.

24:55.020 --> 24:55.960
Let me see you out.

24:55.960 --> 24:56.440
No need,

24:56.870 --> 24:57.970
stay with Yan Ling.

24:58.440 --> 24:59.700
It's the least I can do.

25:13.070 --> 25:13.510
Mom.

25:14.510 --> 25:14.830
Mom.

25:15.640 --> 25:17.290
-Ling, help me!
-Mom.

25:51.310 --> 25:55.080
[Respectfully offered
by student Du Hong in mourning.]

25:57.200 --> 25:59.400
Please accept my deepest condolences.

25:59.550 --> 26:00.110
Uncle.

26:01.780 --> 26:03.450
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:03.450 --> 26:05.650
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:12.080 --> 26:14.280
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:14.550 --> 26:16.510
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:16.510 --> 26:18.710
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:19.250 --> 26:20.910
[A loving mother]

26:19.310 --> 26:21.510
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:21.590 --> 26:23.310
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:23.310 --> 26:25.510
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:25.880 --> 26:28.080
Please accept my deepest condolences.

26:33.200 --> 26:35.040
[Tomb of Loving Father Yan Qianhe
and Loving Mother Su Ruiqin]

27:06.150 --> 27:07.630
[Doctor of Lihai University]

27:07.650 --> 27:09.290
[Honored with the title
of Outstanding Young Academic Worker]

27:25.090 --> 27:25.920
[In Memoriam]

27:25.970 --> 27:26.780
[Doctor of Lihai University]

27:26.810 --> 27:28.020
[Honored with the title
of Outstanding Young Academic Worker]

27:29.240 --> 27:31.550
[Campus Hall of Fame]

28:04.250 --> 28:06.200
[Tomb of Loving Father Yan Qianhe
and Loving Mother Su Ruiqin]

28:41.270 --> 28:43.640
Am I dreaming?

28:51.770 --> 28:52.970
You're not dreaming.

28:54.550 --> 28:56.010
Mom has gone to be with Dad.

28:59.240 --> 29:01.090
Why?

29:05.640 --> 29:07.110
Why?

29:08.920 --> 29:10.910
But she had already forgiven me.

29:15.350 --> 29:17.550
She told me I must live on fully.

29:20.880 --> 29:22.240
I listened to her.

29:23.790 --> 29:24.440
I know.

29:24.800 --> 29:26.870
Mom had forgiven me.

29:27.510 --> 29:28.250
I know.

29:30.510 --> 29:31.250
I know.

29:32.590 --> 29:33.650
Don't be like this.

29:33.890 --> 29:36.170
It was an accident. It was an accident.

29:37.000 --> 29:37.440
It was an accident.

29:37.440 --> 29:39.090
Why did she have to leave?

29:39.160 --> 29:41.000
I don't want this...

29:41.790 --> 29:42.850
Don't be like this.

29:43.240 --> 29:44.680
She would never have wanted to leave you.

29:44.680 --> 29:45.740
Don't be like this.

29:46.070 --> 29:47.270
It wasn't her choice.

29:47.940 --> 29:49.160
It wasn't her choice.

29:49.760 --> 29:50.760
You still have us.

29:51.400 --> 29:52.600
You still have Jiale.

29:54.400 --> 29:55.460
We won't leave you,

29:55.550 --> 29:56.140
okay?

29:56.240 --> 29:57.300
We won't leave you.

30:03.400 --> 30:04.130
I'm here.

30:22.030 --> 30:23.110
I'm right here.

30:52.640 --> 30:53.750
Wait for us at home.

31:42.740 --> 31:46.580
[Lihai City; Unknown Incoming Call]

31:52.030 --> 31:52.590
Hello?

31:52.680 --> 31:53.270
Ms. Su?

31:55.590 --> 31:57.160
No, this isn't Ms. Su.

31:58.510 --> 32:00.270
This is Yan Ling, Ms. Su's daughter.

32:00.270 --> 32:01.240
May I ask who's calling?

32:01.240 --> 32:02.570
I used to be her student.

32:02.830 --> 32:04.830
Last week, Ms. Su called and asked me

32:04.830 --> 32:05.640
to check on a student

32:05.640 --> 32:07.960
from the Class of 2004
at Tianfu Medical University,

32:07.960 --> 32:08.900
named Luo Liang.

32:09.110 --> 32:09.960
I looked it up,

32:10.570 --> 32:12.570
and indeed, there is such a student.

32:12.790 --> 32:15.740
He came from Jingxiong, Diannan,
and was enrolled in 2004.

32:15.740 --> 32:17.140
He was quite remarkable—

32:17.750 --> 32:19.480
both his parents had passed away,

32:19.480 --> 32:20.680
and he was raised by the village,

32:20.680 --> 32:23.940
yet he still managed to achieve
such outstanding results.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.410
What did you say?

32:28.110 --> 32:29.780
Both parents passed away?

32:31.600 --> 32:33.350
Ms. Su specifically asked me

32:33.590 --> 32:35.590
to look into his family background.

32:36.030 --> 32:37.920
His college entrance exam file states

32:37.920 --> 32:39.120
that he was an orphan.

32:51.750 --> 32:52.680
I'm home,

32:59.200 --> 32:59.960
Honey.

33:07.400 --> 33:08.110
Honey?

33:25.680 --> 33:27.710
Let's sort through these another day,

33:27.710 --> 33:28.230
no rush.

33:36.480 --> 33:37.080
Come here.

33:48.850 --> 33:51.430
I've never seen any photos
of you as a child.

33:54.520 --> 33:57.180
There are a few back at my hometown,
but not many.

33:57.750 --> 33:59.190
I moved around a lot for school and work,

33:59.190 --> 34:00.050
and I lost them.

34:03.740 --> 34:05.740
There's something I need to ask you.

34:07.430 --> 34:08.090
What is it?

34:10.070 --> 34:10.800
That person

34:12.690 --> 34:14.550
we met at the restaurant that day—

34:16.340 --> 34:18.139
was she your biological mother?

34:22.179 --> 34:23.199
What do you mean?

34:34.280 --> 34:35.580
I got a call

34:36.280 --> 34:38.340
from one of my mom's former students.

34:40.469 --> 34:42.010
He said my mom had asked him

34:42.610 --> 34:45.139
to check your
college entrance exam records—

34:45.929 --> 34:47.139
and it stated

34:47.850 --> 34:50.050
that both your parents had passed away,

34:50.290 --> 34:51.620
that you were an orphan.

34:59.340 --> 35:00.540
You investigated me?

35:01.550 --> 35:02.400
Not me,

35:02.670 --> 35:03.590
it was Mom.

35:04.660 --> 35:06.060
But that's not the point.

35:07.200 --> 35:09.290
I want to know what's really going on.

35:10.890 --> 35:11.650
The father

35:12.010 --> 35:13.540
who just passed away in May,

35:14.180 --> 35:16.020
and the mother I just met—

35:16.590 --> 35:17.630
who are they?

35:19.590 --> 35:21.390
Are they your adoptive parents?

35:22.930 --> 35:24.420
Why did you lie to me?

35:25.670 --> 35:28.270
I really didn't expect you guys
to be like this.

35:28.800 --> 35:29.480
You don't even

35:29.480 --> 35:31.610
care about the basic trust between us.

35:33.030 --> 35:34.690
What else is there left to say?

35:36.070 --> 35:37.030
Trust?

35:38.840 --> 35:41.120
Isn't trust built on mutual honesty?

35:41.280 --> 35:43.250
Just tell me the truth.

35:45.630 --> 35:46.960
I know you're grieving

35:46.960 --> 35:48.280
your mom's sudden passing,

35:48.280 --> 35:49.200
and so am I.

35:49.360 --> 35:50.070
I don't want to say anything

35:50.070 --> 35:51.960
that would hurt you or her.

35:52.740 --> 35:53.800
But what you did—

35:53.800 --> 35:55.400
investigating behind my back—

35:55.400 --> 35:56.730
it feels shameful to me.

35:57.880 --> 35:58.810
I'm hurt.

35:59.120 --> 35:59.920
Don't walk away.

35:59.920 --> 36:00.650
Talk to me.

36:00.920 --> 36:01.880
What happened?

36:01.880 --> 36:02.630
I want to know.

36:02.630 --> 36:03.400
Tell me.

36:03.400 --> 36:03.920
Tell me!

36:03.920 --> 36:04.920
-Let me pass.
-Don't go.

36:04.920 --> 36:06.250
Just give me some space.

36:06.920 --> 36:07.520
Luo Liang.

36:07.960 --> 36:08.560
Luo Liang!

36:09.660 --> 36:10.410
Luo Liang!

36:14.670 --> 36:15.270
Luo Liang,

36:16.480 --> 36:17.280
open the door.

36:18.140 --> 36:20.470
Come out and talk to me, please,
Luo Liang.

36:24.070 --> 36:26.730
Whatever you're going through,
you can tell me.

36:28.190 --> 36:29.000
I believe you must

36:29.000 --> 36:31.060
have had your reasons for doing this.

36:32.750 --> 36:35.880
But avoiding me like this—
what kind of attitude is that?

36:37.480 --> 36:38.210
Luo Liang,

36:38.860 --> 36:40.720
if you refuse to tell me anything,

36:41.630 --> 36:44.160
how are we supposed
to move forward together?

37:56.150 --> 37:56.810
Keep going!

37:57.120 --> 37:58.580
Feng, where are you going?

37:59.030 --> 37:59.960
What a buzzkill!

38:00.490 --> 38:02.090
Whatever. Let's keep going.

38:04.030 --> 38:05.020
I've actually been

38:05.020 --> 38:07.480
planning to look for you
these past few days.

38:08.570 --> 38:09.970
I killed someone for you,

38:10.590 --> 38:11.290
didn't I?

38:20.650 --> 38:22.110
If you want me to trust you,

38:23.070 --> 38:25.000
show me what you're capable of.

38:26.650 --> 38:27.970
Consider this a test.

38:42.830 --> 38:43.950
Just moving a sign?

38:44.310 --> 38:45.240
That's all?

38:46.460 --> 38:47.610
That's all.

39:01.370 --> 39:06.340
[Construction Ahead, No Entry]

39:13.990 --> 39:15.370
[Construction Ahead, No Entry]

39:50.110 --> 39:50.840
To be honest,

39:50.840 --> 39:52.440
I was really scared at first.

39:52.800 --> 39:54.450
I stayed out of town for many days

39:54.450 --> 39:56.110
and didn't dare to contact you.

39:56.110 --> 39:57.170
Then I saw the news—

39:57.920 --> 40:00.330
it actually got written off
as an accident.

40:00.710 --> 40:01.940
Just a warning sign,

40:02.320 --> 40:04.790
and you took
out your mother-in-law that easily.

40:04.790 --> 40:06.300
But how did you make sure

40:06.710 --> 40:07.880
she showed up exactly

40:07.880 --> 40:09.190
where you wanted?

40:11.280 --> 40:12.070
Impressive.

40:25.070 --> 40:26.110
I know who she is.

40:28.760 --> 40:30.420
When I was searching the news,

40:30.590 --> 40:31.920
I saw you

40:32.560 --> 40:34.070
and Ms. Yan in the scene photos

40:34.070 --> 40:36.480
and found
out the deceased's surname was Su.

40:36.480 --> 40:37.710
Previously, that incident between Ms. Yan

40:37.710 --> 40:39.130
and the CEO of Oceanvision International

40:39.130 --> 40:40.650
blew up online—

40:40.920 --> 40:42.910
her personal info was everywhere.

40:44.480 --> 40:46.670
Her mother's surname was also Su,

40:47.710 --> 40:49.640
to be specific, the full name was Su

40:49.670 --> 40:50.070
Rui

40:51.110 --> 40:51.590
qin.

40:54.510 --> 40:55.910
You figured all that out—

40:56.030 --> 40:57.560
feeling proud of yourself?

40:59.430 --> 41:01.630
Aren't you afraid I'll go to the police?

41:05.480 --> 41:06.400
Why would I be?

41:07.880 --> 41:09.740
You're the one who moved the sign.

41:09.920 --> 41:11.580
What does it have to do with me?

41:17.320 --> 41:18.580
Just kidding, Mister.

41:19.120 --> 41:19.920
Don't worry,

41:20.590 --> 41:22.480
this is my proof of loyalty to you.

41:23.840 --> 41:25.170
But I'm really curious—

41:25.430 --> 41:26.940
why did you want her dead?

41:27.590 --> 41:28.570
Taking a life

41:29.100 --> 41:30.320
just to control Ms. Yan—

41:30.320 --> 41:32.180
is it really worth going that far?

41:37.050 --> 41:38.010
Human life

41:38.900 --> 41:40.430
in essence, is no different

41:41.000 --> 41:42.440
from the flowers, plants,

41:42.440 --> 41:44.000
or earthworms in the soil.

41:45.310 --> 41:46.440
When the time comes,

41:46.710 --> 41:47.640
death will come.

41:48.320 --> 41:51.520
Whether it's this accident
or that one, it's inevitable.

41:52.670 --> 41:54.000
The only difference is,

41:55.840 --> 41:57.510
who pulls the trigger—

41:59.110 --> 42:00.000
fate or us,

42:01.840 --> 42:03.190
ordinary people.

42:06.710 --> 42:07.660
So,

42:07.960 --> 42:11.020
would you be willing to teach me
how to pull the trigger?

42:15.110 --> 42:16.640
Help me with one more thing.

42:18.440 --> 42:22.900
[The Dark Romance]

42:25.190 --> 42:27.320
It's fixed. Try not to get it wet again.

42:29.150 --> 42:30.070
I'll give you a discount.

42:30.070 --> 42:30.670
That'll be 260.

42:30.670 --> 42:31.670
You can scan here.

42:31.770 --> 42:33.250
[Ms. Su, tomorrow at 10 AM,]

42:33.280 --> 42:35.530
[same supermarket, let's have a chat.]

42:35.600 --> 42:37.220
[Delete]

42:37.240 --> 42:38.360
[Are you sure
you want to delete this message?]

42:42.220 --> 42:42.730
[Are you sure
you want to delete this message?]

42:42.760 --> 42:43.860
[Delete]

42:44.100 --> 42:45.040
[All Messages]
